Woke up today, Thinking about the importance of listening. Just that.

Listening to your friends better and your family and the people around you. 
Sometimes they are trying to say something that they can’t find the words for or that they are  scared of saying out loud.
There’s so much that hasn’t been said out loud, because people are scared and because so many people don’t really listen.
It’s so important to take a step back and think less about ourselves and open up our eyes and ears more to the people around us.
Sometimes they need you more than they can admit. And sometimes all they need is for someone to listen to them, really listen to what’s really going on on the inside. 💗

I remember going to @kobebryant s last game like it was yesterday.. 50 points. He was a true legend and his mentality was beyond inspiring. This is so heartbreaking.. sending my condolences and prayers to his wife, family and friends.. 💔💗💗 #mambamentality

I haven’t really worked out for the past month because I was travelling a lot and during Christmas time I like to not stress myself too much about it and to just take some time off. Now I’m ready to get back into it, as working out really makes me feel  great  mentally and physically. @define.london is one of my favorite workouts to tone up, but I’m not going to lie it wasn’t an easy session today haha but pushed through and ready to get stronger again 💪🏼🤗
